version_description:
* Made levels require memorization less, should be more skill based now.
* Only one in-app now, premium.
* Fixed a few crashes and bugs

• Improve controls, more responsive now
• Make it possible to move left and right when in air
• Performance optimizations
• Fixed bug where game wouldn't start in 60 fps mode if selected
• Tweaked some levels
• Updated translations

• Classic+ game mode, new remixed levels
• Blitz and Blitz+ game modes, play all levels in a row and get as far as possible for a high score
• Improved controls and sound effects for movement
• Bug fixes & Optimizations
